rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I think we Phonexes in Superbia
are thin.

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's a harsh land where we can hardly find any
of our favorite grasses or insects...

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But we're still alive...
with our strong life force.

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Huh?
We don't look much different from other Phonexes?

rows.label: tlk42100151_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I don't believe it!
My stomach is always
grumbling.
